#greatwhiteshark- “ It’s in there somewhere, let me have another look.” - The Big Lebowski 
We are back from Australia and I’m at loss for words. Amazing weather, incredible sharks and getting to shoot along side the legendary Andrew Fox.  It’s all we could have hoped for. The crew and the vessel -The Rodney Fox- was awesome and we are so grateful for their professionalism, expertise and care for the sharks. 
Excited to return.

A huge Mako shark the size of an adult Great White shark gives us a great view at how their floating jaw system works. 
They can extend their top jaw far from their skull making it possible for them to reach out and catch some of the fastest fish in the ocean. 
- 🎥 @joeromeiro333
